data.description: Experience this luxurious masterpiece nestled in sought after Woodbury Place neighborhood in Auburn, Georgia convenient to Chateau Elan Winery and Resort and Hamilton Mill Country Club.  A stunning beautifully crafted exterior 3 sides brick residence with capturing landscaping offering the epitome of refined living. Boasting an impressive 4493 square feet of meticulously designed space, this residence exudes sophistication and elegance at every turn.    Step inside to discover a harmonious blend of opulence and functionality. The expansive floor plan effortlessly accommodates 7 bedrooms, providing ample space for both privacy and communal living. The 5 meticulously crafted bathrooms showcase modern fixtures and lavish finishes, creating a spa-like atmosphere for ultimate relaxation.    This residence is truly a haven for those who appreciate the finer things in life. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, custom cabinetry, and exquisite countertops. Entertain guests in style with the spacious living and dining areas, adorned with a fireplace, high ceilings and an abundance of natural light.    The allure of this home extends beyond its main levels, as it encompasses a sprawling 1966 square foot basement. This versatile space offers endless possibilities, complete with full eat in kitchen, 2 bedrooms, and 1 full bath, laundry room, second bedroom being used as a gym/game room, office and a storm/fallout shelter. The basement also has a storage room with oversized doors housing lawn equipment and grills that can be driven or easily rolled out to support a full walkout basement to a beautiful serene patio connected to a large backyard.    Indulge in the outdoor oasis that surrounds this residence, featuring meticulously landscaped grounds, a cozy deck partially enclosed and partially outdoors. Take the deck steps downstairs to access the patio uniquely made into a private retreat, allowing residents to bask in the tranquility of their own sanctuary.    Elegance, comfort, and grandeur define this exceptional property. Experience the pinnacle of luxury living in this meticulously crafted home that seamlessly blends timeless design with modern amenities. Welcome to a residence where every detail has been thoughtfully considered, creating a lifestyle of unparalleled sophistication.
